citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T00:42:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港成班冚家挪住外國護照既大愛支，仲要班後生燒多幾多青春，去為一個一早燈紅酒綠紙醉金迷既遠方城市哭喪自瀆？？？</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote>當年中國64<br />\n如果無香港人傷亡<br />\n香港駛唔駛年年攪咁多活動悼念<br />\n全球無一個地方好似香港大陣象</blockquote>大中華膠多 個時好多都對中國有幻想有希望</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要悼念，班大愛支係咪最應該為六四後仲支持民主回西路樓死先呢？？？尤其個班之後冚家攞定護照走既！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"60a9d00a73cdd15a3e6fed1d3354d881c66c3866","tid":688983,"uid":87780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T00:48:21.000Z","msg":"平你老母閪<br />\n香港墮落到變做中國二線城市仲喺度搞中國人集氣活動"}]}